# Engramia — empty extras placeholder.
#
# Mounted at /etc/caddy/extras.caddy by environments that have no
# extra site blocks beyond the universal api + app pair (test, train,
# local dev).
#
# Keeping this file empty-but-present lets the base Caddyfile use a
# single unconditional `import /etc/caddy/extras.caddy` directive
# across every environment.
